title: 3 Pack Steel Wool, 3.2”x7.5 Ft Control Fill Fabric, Gap Blocker for Holes, Pipeline, Wall Crack, House, Garage Including DIY Accessories, One Pair of Gloves and Scissor
features: SUPERIOR QUALITY STEEL WOOL: Say goodbye to low-quality, brittle steel wool that breaks apart and leaves behind debris. Our steel wool is carefully designed to provide a robust rodent barrier and is made of high-grade materials that won't rust or disintegrate when pressure is applied. Prevent critters with MAPORCH's steel wool and enjoy peace of mind knowing you're using a reliable, long-lasting solution.

EASY-TO-USE, VERSATILE SOLUTION: We understand the frustrations of dealing with rodents in your home, so we've designed our steel wool to be easily moldable, allowing you to fill gaps and holes of various shapes and sizes for optimal rodent prevention. Our 3.2" x 7.5 ft rolls make it simple to create an effective mice control barrier in no time, without the hassle.

KEEP YOUR HOME RODENT-FREE: Don't let rodents take over your home or office – our steel wool offers top-of-the-line protection from pesky intruders. By filling gaps and holes around pipes, duct systems, windows, and walls, you'll create a strong rodent barrier that keeps citters out, ensuring you can live and work in comfort.

WE BELIEVE IN EFFECTIVE, SIMPLE SOLUTIONS: At MAPORCH, we stand for quality products that make your life easier. Our steel wool solution is designed to be not only highly effective but also easy to use, ensuring you can quickly protect your home or office without any complicated processes or expensive exterminators.

THE COMPLETE PACKAGE FOR PROFESSIONAL RESULTS: Enjoy the convenience of our included premium cut-resistant gloves and stainless steel scissors in your pursuit of a rodent-free environment. Our mission is to provide you with a comprehensive solution that not only keeps rodents at bay but also offers the necessary tools to ensure an easy, hassle-free installation process.
description: Product Description Steel Wool To Seal Holes for Mice Wire Mesh Mice Hole Filler Protect Your Home from the Outside In Maporch's Grade 4 Low Carbon High Manganese Wire Wool is the easiest way to defend your home from unwelcome visitors. The thick strands of wire mesh hold strong in gaps around pipes, vents, and cracks. However the low carbon of the fine wire wool means it's also flexible, so it won’t snap or crumble in tiny spaces. And thanks to the high manganese, your mouse mesh won't break down with time, or their teeth. Complete Kit With Gloves & Scissors Keeping mice out has never been easier! Our steel wool mice blocker kit has everything you need; thick grip gloves, heavy-duty scissors, and 3 rolls of tough wire wool mice material. Just follow three simple steps: find the gaps, cut the wool to size, and fill them in! Our durable wire mesh to keep mice out gives you a strong, reliable barrier against pests. Quick, easy, and effective protection for your home! Gap Fillers for Mice & More
